Sylvain Simard suggested that the four firms that make up the consortium (BPR, Dessau, Groupe SM and Axor) are &quot;well known to the Liberal Party of Quebec&quot;.
Minister Normandeau dropped that the PQ is also linked to these firms which “finance” it, before specifying that it was rather its leaders.
